Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:06.23,Black Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(906,346)}Michiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi, don't forget us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all so lively. {mengomengo - that sounds awful}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best over there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll write to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come by now and then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go finding yourself a girlfriend, Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And just like that, the person who I loved was transferring schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we made more memories...\N even though we didn't talk very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Michiyo, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, your aunt is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, Michiyo{idk if you want to do anything with the name}, as lively as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing again? Basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, she does{jiguro?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's so tall, what a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's just for show. She's just unsteady when she plays sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who she got that from...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako, you can't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how I am. A plain old bean pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See, she got mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, she'll get over it soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how did Togashi's goodbye party go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko and Yuuko stated to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You always {\i1}really{\i0} liked Togashi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear that, why don't you say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts! I'm sorry, just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's it cute? Auntie handed it down to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it would be too short for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it wouldn't suit me, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame you're that tall, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be cuter if I was more ladylike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'd be able to get on better with Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll forget all about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts... {i've skipped all the "are... are..." bits }
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fever isn't going down at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to stay in bed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll speak to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She must've been really shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you should try and get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The boy she likes has transferred schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! I didn't think she had someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she wanted him to notice her\N she should have been more lady like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's always you who buys me boyish clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiyo, we're going shopping, so stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, nobody's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the stamp. {that's what a hanko is right? lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"From Togashi to Kakimoto Michiyo."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Togashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"How are you, Kakimoto?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sure you'll be surprised that this turned up out of the blue."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've moved in with my grandma in the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but my grandma is ill, and before she\N passes she wants to see the girl I'll marry."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{boku ni oyome san nante hayasugiru kara, mitakereba nagai kishite kurette itan dakedo, kikanain da}{probably wrong...}  "It's too soon for me to get married and I\N keep telling her that, but she doesn't listen."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{also probably wrong} "So, my grandma has sent this\N one piece. It's very special to her."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sorry if this is late notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but can you wear this and meet me at the Usakuracho{? - spoken again at 8;07} bus station at 2 p.m. this Sunday?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're the only person I can count on."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't like yatta...    therefore 'liberal' woo} I can't believe it. It suits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure picked up quickly. {idk if that sounds weird - was kinda 'guessy'}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can all go shopping tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a promise with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me something back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I could be late getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write Chinatsu a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"To Chinatsu, I've actually gone to see Togashi. - Michiyo{don't know which name is written <_<}"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She still isn't back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's late, it's getting dark too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try phoning one of her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The address book...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to get told off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Akiko? This is\N Kakimoto Michiyo's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have Togashi's phone number? {skipping the bit about him being the 'transferred' togashi}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Kakimoto was off yesterday so she wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He was really unlucky, he was caught up in a big crash when he was moving house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,His whole family died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Kakimoto, are you there?\N Was it something about Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I knew she wasn't coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have been searching for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but they've made the public know\N that there aren't any leads on it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was one story I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a pretty girl wearing a one piece around Usakuracho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She was holding hands with a scruffy looking man, and having lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But those are just rumors, I know they aren't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
